title: favoriteFoodApi

api_list.name: Get All Favorite Food
api_list.description: This endpoint will return all my favorite Cameroonian dishes
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://favoritefoodapi.p.rapidapi.com/food/api/v1/favorites"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "favoritefoodapi.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
